OL,3,CElectricity and gas theft: The hidden
OL,4,Ccrime visible in your energy bill
OL,6,FThis is also about something far more
OL,7,Fimportant than money - energy thieves
OL,8,Foften put lives at risk.
OL,10,FDave Garner, Director of Safety at
OL,11,FCadent, explains the signs of
OL,12,Fpotential gas theft
OL,14,FWe spoke to the mother of Harvey
OL,15,FTyrrell, who died aged seven. An
OL,16,Fenergy thief had tampered with power
OL,17,Fsupplies at the premises where he was
OL,18,Fplaying.
OL,20,FHis mum is battling to raise awareness.
