OL,6,F"All we did as a family was went for
OL,7,Fdinner. And we came home without our
OL,8,Fchild," she said.
OL,10,F"Anyone that's thinking of tampering
OL,11,Fand messing around with things like
OL,12,Felectricity and gas - you can't
OL,13,Fphysically see them, you don't know
OL,14,Fwhat you're dealing with and the risks
OL,15,Fand how dangerous it is."
OL,17,FDanielle is campaigning for the
OL,18,Fenforcement of electrical inspections,
OL,19,Ftesting and certification of pubs.
