OL,3,CElectricity and gas theft: The hidden
OL,4,Ccrime visible in your energy bill
OL,6,FHigh energy prices are being blamed
OL,7,Ffor a dangerous increase in the theft
OL,8,Fof gas and electricity.
OL,10,FThere's been a 55% rise in meter
OL,11,Ftampering as thieves aim to avoid
OL,12,Fpaying for their power supplies.
OL,14,FToday, the industry issued new
OL,15,Fwarnings about the potentially deadly
OL,16,Fdangers.
