OL,3,CElectricity and gas theft: The hidden
OL,4,Ccrime visible in your energy bill
OL,6,FThe sector is urging us to look out
OL,7,Ffor and report signs of theft, but
OL,8,Fthere are big questions about whether
OL,9,Fit is doing enough to save customers
OL,10,Fpaying the cost of other people's
OL,11,Fcrime.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FSigns of electricity theft include
OL,19,Floose or unusual wiring, sparks coming
OL,20,Ffrom the meter or burn marks or
OL,21,Fscorches on the meter.
